{"tid":1423620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「陰謀論」點解簡深水埗拉人 係因為深水埗警署係歷史建築物引你地破壞","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:46:51.000Z","uid":45123,"like":88,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"31e6bf8b126c371ba4b878f9e9357209116cc651","tid":1423620,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"以下係陰謀論：點解咁奇怪冇啦啦行過都拉人？<br />\n點解要簡深水埗？<br />\n因為今日冇咩野講<br />\n萬一你地破壞左深水埗警署 聽日就大把野講<br />\n我都幾肯定 想掉野果啲 一定係<strong>鬼</strong><br />\n因為深水埗街坊冇理由唔知果到係歷史文物<br />\n啲警察仲會係局入面<strong>不斷挑機</strong><br />\n引你地攻擊<br />\n所以大家一定要小心"},{"pid":"c9487c69d71cbc2cffdf2d29c97a550e39f2467c","tid":1423620,"uid":283504,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c372df0a760a8adca693b3d3a17493d93dedcc5f","tid":1423620,"uid":45123,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"c9487c69d71cbc2cffdf2d29c97a550e39f2467c","tid":1423620,"uid":283504,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"Yes <br />\n千其唔好破壞  亦都要阻人破壞<br />\n唔係聽日各大頭條+4點鐘許sir見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12ad879d4a9e291e9ea247963d039df57a1ca49","tid":1423620,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57f3b060d8741caf168734f3e5d981e9678063e5","tid":1423620,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:35:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"422975aab41976ef90b65cdc7505fdb315ad4958","tid":1423620,"uid":258192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"202843b3330937466bb5a0664191dd1dce790dd2","tid":1423620,"uid":81151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re